description: An arcane focus is a special item designed to channel the power of arcane spells. A sorcerer, warlock, or wizard can use such an item as a spellcasting focus.
An arcane focus is a special item designed to channel the power of arcane spells. A sorcerer, warlock, or wizard can use such an item as a spellcasting focus.
Each signet ring has a distinctive design carved into it. When you press this ring into warm sealing wax, you leave an identifying mark.
Training with jeweler's tools includes the basic techniques needed to beautify gems. It also gives you expertise in identifying precious stones.
Stone cutting can refer to cutting and grinding rough, raw stones into workable segments. It is also the act of cutting facets on stones (also known as faceting).
Common gems worth 10 gp include azurite, banded agates, blue quartz, eye agates, hematite, lapis lazuli, malachite, moss agates, obsidian, rhodochrosite, tiger eye and turquoise.
Common gems worth 50 gp include bloodstones, carnelian, chalcedony, chrysoprase, citrines, jaspers, moonstones, onyx, quartz, sardonyx, star rose quartz and zircons.
Common gems worth 100 gp include amber, amethyst, chrysoberyl, coral, garnets, jade, jet, pearl, spinel and tourmaline.
Common gems worth 500 gp include alexandrite, aquamarine, black pearl, blue spinel, peridot and topaz.
Common gems worth 1,000 gp include black opals, blue sapphires, emeralds, fire opals, opals, star rubys, star sapphires and yellow sapphires.
Common gems worth 5,000 gp include black sapphires, diamond, hyacinths and rubies.
